text: Jemma Dessauvagie is an Australian water polo player. She competed for the Australian women's national water polo team in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Success is 'from within' says former Australian water polo player ABC Radio Hobart, 6 March, 2014 Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Australian water polo players
